text: The 2014–15 Botola 2 was the 53rd and current season of Botola 2, the second division of the Moroccan football league. Its started on 23 August 2014 and ended on 4 May 2015. ==Teams== * Association Salé * Chabab Houara * COD Meknès * Ittihad Tanger * JS Kasba Tadla * JS Massira * MC Oujda * Olympique Dcheira * Racing de Casablanca * Raja Beni Mellal * Union Aït Melloul * Union de Mohammédia * US Témara * Wydad de Fès * Wydad Témara * Youssoufia Berrechid ==League table== ==See also== * 2014–15 Botola ==External links== *Fédération Royale Marocaine de Football Category:GNF 2 seasons Moro Category:2014–15 in Moroccan football
